snippet.title: Super Emo Alpaca!! (Also first video lol)((READ DESC))
snippet.description: Hiya! I am Fluffy.Tea a new you tuber I guess. I only post Super Emo Alpaca and MAYBE other games. We shall see! This game is sadly only available on android and is one of my favorite games ever! Super Emo Alpaca is a game where you learn to love even the most ugly things!  The main thing is breeding though! S.E.A. is a really great time killer and if people don't like it that's their loss 👺👺
